{
 "name": "RPlog_To_Kill_A_Mockingbird",
 "title": "To Kill a Mockingbird: A Black Operation Against Caspar",
 "summary": "On the Security Deck of the Super Star Destroyer Nemesis, Lord Thel briefs Imperial Intelligence agent Kelbris Cooper and Stormtrooper Lieutenant Loreck Hawkins on a covert operation against the neutral Caspian Democratic Union. Thel reveals that the CDU has secretly been arming the Rebellion in breach of its treaty of nonaggression, and the Empire needs hard proof of the deception to justify conquering the system. He orders Cooper and Hawkins to establish themselves at the Imperial Embassy on Caspar, locate the warehouse or transport vessel holding the smuggled arms, and infiltrate it without bloodshed or any trail leading back to the Empire. Cooper's bloodthirsty instincts are repeatedly curbed in favor of discretion, and the two officers begin planning a disguised infiltration involving sabotaged climate-control systems to flush out and slice the target facility. The pair are dismissed to prepare their equipment and depart for Caspar.",
